         MACRO ,
&NM      MAPTSA &PFX=TSA,&DSECT=
         GBLC  &ZZZLNM(128)
         GBLB  &ZZZLFG
         GBLA  &ZZZLNO
         LCLC  &P,&N
&P       SETC  '&PFX'
&N       SETC  '&NM'
         AIF   ('&N' NE '').HAVSECT
&N       SETC  'MAP'.'&P'
.HAVSECT AIF   ('&DSECT' EQ 'NO').NOSEC
&N       DSECT ,
         AGO   .COMSEC
.NOSEC   AIF   ('&NM' EQ '').COMSEC
&NM      DS    0D
.COMSEC  ANOP  ,
&P.@SERV DC    A(0)          ADDRESS OF @SERVICE ROUTINE
&P.EXSVC SVC   0             SVC OR BASR TO @SERVICE (TARGET OF EX 0,)
&P.#SIZE DC    AL2(&P.SIZE)  AMOUNT OF STORAGE GOTTEN
&P.FIX@  DC    D'0'          BASE OF FIXED OFFSET WORK AREA ADDRESSES
         SERVWORK OPT=EXPAND  EXPAND FIXED STORAGE SAVERS
&P.SIZE  EQU   *-&P.@SERV    SIZE TO GET
         MEND  ,
